OL,3,CLuxury car thieves jailed after one
OL,4,Cfilmed himself in stolen vehicle
OL,6,FA group of thieves who stole multiple
OL,7,Fluxury cars have been jailed after one
OL,8,Fmember of their group filmed himself
OL,9,Fin a stolen car.
OL,11,FHamza Ghafoor, 22, and five other men
OL,12,Fstole cars worth up to #79,000,
OL,13,Fdriving them in a high speed convoy.
OL,15,FMobile phone footage recorded by
OL,16,FGhafoor, shows him wearing a balaclava
OL,17,Fand revealing he planned to commit a
OL,18,Fburglary. He then films himself
OL,19,Fdriving a BMW.
