OL,3,CLuxury car thieves jailed after one
OL,4,Cfilmed himself in stolen vehicle
OL,6,FLancashire Police has released
OL,7,Fevidence which helped convict the
OL,8,Fgang, who travelled from Bradford to
OL,9,FLancashire to commit nine burglaries
OL,10,Fbetween September and November 2023.
OL,12,FPolice caught the group after two BMWs
OL,13,Fwere stolen from a property in Langho,
OL,14,Fwith telephone evidence linking
OL,15,FGhafoor, along with Mohammed Zubhir,
OL,16,F24, and Dylan Shuttleworth, 18, to the
OL,17,Fcrime.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
