OL,3,CLuxury car thieves jailed after one
OL,4,Cfilmed himself in stolen vehicle
OL,6,FOfficers found a Louis Vuitton bag
OL,7,Fcontaining 926 wraps of crack cocaine
OL,8,Fand 319 wraps of heroin in Ghafoor's
OL,9,Fbedroom when he was arrested.
OL,11,FLancashire Police shared the footage
OL,12,Fto Facebook, with the caption: "The
OL,13,Fman in the footage is Hamza Ghafoor
OL,14,Fand he's not the brightest burglar of
OL,15,Fthe bunch.
OL,17,F"He thought it would be a good idea to
OL,18,Ffilm himself before and after
OL,19,Fcommitting burglaries in East
OL,20,FLancashire during which high value
OL,21,Fcars were stolen.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
