OL,3,CLuxury car thieves jailed after one
OL,4,Cfilmed himself in stolen vehicle
OL,6,F"The joke is on him though, as this
OL,7,Fturned out to be key evidence in
OL,8,Fconvicting him and four others of
OL,9,Fconspiring to commit burglary".
OL,11,FPolice say the gang broke into
OL,12,Fproperties in Pendle, Blackburn, the
OL,13,FRibble Valley, Hyndburn and Chorley to
OL,14,Fsteal the high value vehicles.
OL,16,FThe stolen vehicles include a #79,000
OL,17,FBMW X3, #35,000 Volkswagen Tiguan, an
OL,18,FAudi Q5 and an Audi Q3. A Volkswagen
OL,19,FGolf and Merceded CLA 45 were also
OL,20,Ftaken.
